<div id="banner">
	<h1>Goodbye, Brent.</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Brent Simmons is <a href="http://inessential.com/2002/03/01.html">leaving UserLand</a>. Brent always had a provoking thought, a kind word and a helping hand. I wish him the best of luck in his future endeavors. Brent, many thanks for your code, hosting, support, <a href="http://inessential.com/">blog</a> and <a href="http://mac.scripting.com/">news</a>.</p>

